b'Sore Ike! Zukkoke Sannin-gumi':
b"Based on Nasu Masamoto's Zukkoke Sannin-gumi juvenile novels series.

The main characters are 6 grade boys, Hachibei, Hakase, and Mo-chan. This anime shows their adventures.

(Source: AnimeNfo)"
